  Kinetic (Delta T^0):                  16.208627447283273        441.0592         10171.07         42555.75
  Delta V^Pauli Coulomb:                -8.410808576807177       -228.8697         -5277.86        -22082.57
  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -1.876324474971351        -51.0574         -1177.41         -4926.29
